You observe two distressed-looking ninja gals strapped down to tables, who wriggle and whimper into their gags as they writhe about in their tight stone bonds. One of the women catches your eye with her greyish blue hair with white highlights. Her purple eyes also stand out, especially with how wide open they are. Wearing a ninja outfit that has left her midriff and legs completely exposed, she is forced to endure countless feathers swishing over her exposed skin. From her feet to her belly, there isn't a part of her that isn't getting tickled. For such a tough-looking tomboy, her face is surprisingly cute when smiling.
Hey, these two look kinda familiar.
Don’t they all look kinda familiar?

You look over to the other girl, a slender, dark-haired ninja and see that she is in very much a similar situation. You can only see one eye as her hair is covering the other, but that eye looks very much imperilled. Feathers cover her bare skin as well, acting almost as a second covering of sorts. You look up to the sign and see that the objective of this one is to make the lee pass out. An hourglass is nearby, ready to turn once someone starts.
Well, look on the bright side, ladies. After we win, you get a break!

The feathers recede as you get into position. Left gasping and giggling, the women appear to be on the verge of exhaustion and the one before you tries to speak through her gag. At most, she makes a soft, mumbling sound that could be her trying to beg for mercy, but it's hard to tell.
I assume you’re saying you understand what we’re trying to do and support us. In which case, thank you!

Ignoring the ninja's attempts to speak, you look down to her feet. The dark-haired ninja's feet are smaller, positively petite in fact, topped with pudgy black-painted toes and are a very tempting target. The other woman's feet are a bit bigger, but no less soft looking and with toes that just begging to be teased.

Torn between two delightful targets, you opt for the grey-haired ninja. Longer feet do offer more to tickle, after all. Cissy stands by the black-haired girl and grins as she wiggles her fingers in front of her eyes. Both women look utterly exhausted, but as you both prepare to dig your fingers into their ticklish skin, you find they have energy enough to tense up in fearful anticipation. Now, where to begin?

You move down to the ninja's feet, deciding to do everything you can to knock her out. You pop her toes into your mouth and begin to lick and nibble over them while your fingers scratch madly over the soles. The ninja goes into silent laughter. Her body shakes and heaves, but there's nothing left to give. You rake your fingers up and down the soles as your teeth gently nibble over the digits while the tomboyish ninja girl howls with laughter. You know she won’t be able to last long now — she simply can’t breathe enough just using her nose.

Cissy has chosen a different tactic for her target. Her fingers unleash a wild, frenzied, tickle attack against the captive. Her fingers attack all over the soles and tops of the ninja’s petite feet. No spot goes untouched as the frantic tickling moves over the bare skin constantly.

You start with the ninja's midriff, wriggling your fingers across her belly. She lets out a strained laugh through her gag as the ticklish sensations escalate, though you've only just started. You can see that the ninja is already greatly weakened from her earlier torment. Once your fingers start targeting her navel, her face grows red and you feel certain she’s on the verge.

Cissy has a similar idea as she goes for the bare thighs of her target. The soft skin of the legs proves to be easy places to tickle as her fingers crawl up and down the insides of the thighs. The reaction from the dark-haired ninja is intense, her hair flying in every direction as she squeals and squeaks into the gag.
You pick up a black feather and a white feather from the ground. These feathers sprang in the air and tickled the ninja gals before, but they don’t seem to be ‘activated’ right now.
Think it’ll be alright if we borrow these?
Try, bro. I’m sure they’ll tickle you silly if the answer is no.

With a bit of trepidation, you pick up a few feathers, but you’re pleased to see your fears are unfounded. You put your feathers to work, exploring the curves of the ninja girl’s arches and the pads of their toes. The blue-haired girl is pretty squirmy, so her pale feet keep on scrunching and dodging, but you follow them wherever they go. Tears well in her eyes and sweat trickles down her cheek as you keep on feathering and feathering.
Seems to be working well. Pass me a few plumes, bro?

Tittering, Cissy takes a feather, pulls back black-haired ninja girl’s big toe and weaves the feather all over the sole, targeting the extended arch. When Cissy releases that digit, the black-painted toes scrunch at once, but they soon start flailing and splaying again once Cissy introduces the feather to her armpits. The soft bristles of the feather flutter into one underarm while Cissy’s long nails dig into the other, and the ninja girl’s eyelids are fluttering as the sensations start to overwhelm her.

Your efforts prove to be enough to push the ninja over the edge, and she soon slumps down, completely unconscious. Moments later, with a final flurry of tickling across the black-haired ninja girl’s petite feet, Cissy finishes up too. That ninja gives one final cry of muffled laughter before her eyes roll to the back of her head and she passes out. Time to check the scoreboard!
Just about snuck that one through.
Yeah. And as a bonus, these two can have a break...
A bucket appears over each woman, tipping over and dousing them in cold water. They wake up with muffled screams as feathers appear over their bodies once more.
You look and Cissy and shrug, unable to really do anything right now as the tickling starts again. Maybe they'll get an actual break the next time they pass out, but you doubt it. C’est la vie.
Well, I think that’s all the stalls I can see. Maybe see if we’ve caught the Tickle Lords’ attention?
Luci and Raph... I wonder what kind of people we’re dealing with.
Feel like I can't get enough of seeing these two tickled.

This stall has a green-clad ninja upon a platform, with her restrained body on the level of your chest as she's tied down. Just below the feet are two buckets of soapy water and toothbrushes, and you barely even have to look at the nearby sign in order to realise what you have to do. Clean those feet of every spot of ink and you win. A small hourglass is nearby, alerting you to the fact that this will be timed as well. A quick glance at the scoreboard informs you of the time to beat.

You sit down and the quills pull from away from the ninja's feet. She manages to catch your words and lets out a high-pitched whimper. Her digits are splashed all over with ink, and even the tops of her feet have a few splotches. Her toenails get this as well, covered with the ink and hiding the shade of green that the ninja had originally painted them with. You pick up the brushes, and dunk them into the water as Cissy does the same. The hourglass turns over and the sand begins to fall, and both of you start scrubbing away at the ink.

The ninja girl reacts violently to the tickling of the brushes. She twists and strains even as the stone shackles bite into her joint and screams into the gag as the bristles scrape over her soles. If it weren't obvious before that she's deathly sensitive on her feet, it is now. Every movement of the brushes provokes another scream as you clean and tickle her feet at the same time.
Starting to be grateful she’s gagged. She’s a screechy one, isn’t she?

You nod and ponder your next move.

The soft flesh of her milky soles is beginning to turn a shade of pink from the incessant stroking of the toothbrushes. You continue cleaning and give the odd glance towards the hourglass. You’re not sure, but it seems like the sand is falling faster than it should have been.

You and Cissy put all into your efforts of cleaning the arches and the centres of the soles, where most of the ink is. The brushes in your hands are a blur as they move across the arches, heels and balls to get at the odd splotch of ink there. The green-clad ninja would have been wailing like a banshee, had she been able to. But, even with the gag, her maddened laughter is clear. With the high-pitches she’s able to hit, you imagine she’d make a great popstar with such a vocal range.

The stiff bristles of the brush are thin enough to get between the ninja's long toes, allowing you to clean every spot there as well. Doing so earns you the most frantic screams and laughter from the ninja, but you manage to clean away the last of the ink from her toes after a bit of spirited scrubbing.
There, now we can admire those pretty green toes of yours? Isn’t that nice?

Ah, cramp! Gotta rest my hand...
